  <category name="AI voice tools">
    <reapack name="reasonate.lua" type="script" desc="Reasonate - AI voice tools (TTS, voice replacement, dubbing, repair, SFX and music)">
      <metadata>
        <description><![CDATA[
AI audio production toolkit for REAPER built on the ElevenLabs API:
text to speech (single voice and multi-speaker dialogue), voice
replacement on recorded takes, dubbing into other languages, word-level
repair of recordings, and sound effects / music generation - all
non-destructive, all inside REAPER.

Requires ReaImGui 0.10+ (via ReaPack), the SWS extension (in-app
previews) and your own ElevenLabs API key. Optional: an LLM API key
for dubbing translation and scene analysis. By falami.studio (b4s1c), MIT.
]]></description>
        <link rel="website">https://falami.studio</link>
        <link rel="donation">https://ko-fi.com/quickmd</link>
      </metadata>
